<title>
Side Turn Signal Light Removal and Installation (If Equipped)
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B9206006001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Unlock a hook (3) by moving the side turn signal light in directions “1”, “2” and “3” in sequence as shown in figure. Then remove side turn signal light (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect connector (2) from side turn signal light.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Side turn signal light cannot be disassembled. Replace side turn signal light as a unit when bulb is blown or lens is broken.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
